summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of product catalogue application. All major features working correctly including dark theme, division switching, navigation, import wizard, and Supabase integration.
passed_tests: Dashboard page loads correctly with dark theme
Division switcher toggles between APT (green) and HOSPI (red) themes successfully
Products page displays product catalog with 5 products and proper table structure
Import wizard page loads with all 4 stages displayed correctly
File dropzone accepts Excel files (.xlsx, .xls) with proper validation
Sidebar navigation works for all pages (Dashboard, Products, Quotations, Customers, Import History, Settings)
Settings page displays division information correctly
Supabase integration working - products data loads successfully
APT and HOSPI theme switching works across all pages
All interactive elements have proper data-testid attributes for testing
